The paper discusses recent advances in network acceleration, compression, and accelerator design for deep neural networks, which are primarily used in computer vision applications (cs.CV). The paper also covers topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), augmented reality (cs.AR), and systems and control (cs.SY) as they relate to network acceleration and hardware design.
